data.oai_dc:dc: This file contains phylogenetic information for taxa in this study. The "name" column matches taxa names used in the study. i.e. not all taxa are resolved to the same level, and this is used to access other phylogenetic information. The "minimum.res.method" and "minimum.con.method" are specific to the WebBuilder analysis. See main text for more details.
